      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Maaaan... Time sure does fly.</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> (It was before the Pymon Mercenaries went to Kyle Draum…)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
