   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-e" mid="79" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>But weren't you with a bunch of merchants then?</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(I took a few random guard missions with him.) </FONT><FONT color=#662500>But what brought you here?</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Joining a group of bandits is odd enough, but what made him a wanted man?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-f" mid="80" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>It was a personal matter!<BR>Speaking of which, you are just as sneaky as ever and I can't think of a single redeeming quality that you possess!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-g" mid="81" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>But what brings you here?<BR>You're definitely not the person I came here to see.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-h" mid="82" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#662500>(Takes out the wanted poster and Maisa's letter.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Oh, right. Maisa asked me to deliver this.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>But I didn't know you were the one I'd be delivering it to.<BR>Did you really kill a Child?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-i" mid="83" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>I did indeed, though I ended up losing most of my power and had no choice but to run away from the Childs that followed...<BR>It was a pathetic end.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-j" mid="84" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm a mercenary. I'm up for the job as long as the pay is good. What did you want me to do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>Anyway, this poster... Apparently someone is after me despite my best efforts to play dead....<BR>Do you think you can help me, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>?<BR>
Maisa said she'd pay for the mission.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-k" mid="85" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>I'm a member of the bandits in the citadel here. <BR>As their sub-captain, the only one who will be able to take me out is the captain himself.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-2-l" mid="86" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>Even so, sometimes a blind squirrel finds a nut.<BR>So, just in case, could you retrieve the wanted posters from the other bandits<BR>and put up these revised wanted posters in highly visible areas?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3060_lapis-3" mid="87" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That sounds simple enough.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3060_lapis-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>Thanks for taking the job. And... Thank you for helping me back then, too.<BR>The next time we meet, it won't be me asking you for help.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2244_place-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2244_place-5" mid="88" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#662500>(Shall I post one here?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Suitable Place$<BR>The area in front is well-exposed, so this should be highly visible for all to see.</html>]]></talk_question>
