   <talk_paragraph index="n2244_place-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Okay, time to return to Rhadames.<BR></FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>※ Go to Rhadames and meet with Manager Maisa.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-a" mid="90" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>You're back. So, what do you think now that you saw the truth for yourself?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-b" mid="91" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It's surprising enough to see someone in person who was thought to be dead,<BR>but more amazing is that he thought he was supposed to be meeting you.</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>What is this all about?</FONT><FONT color=#662500>? </FONT><FONT color=#662500>Hadar seems unaware that Lapis is still alive.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-b" image="QN_Kali.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-c" mid="92" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>Well… To be honest, there was an adventurer who came here a while ago to kill Lapis.<BR>I don't think she was specifically hired by President Vernicka,<BR>but she seemed to be trying to help him out.<BR>Anyway, when push came to shove and she actually found Lapis, she let him get away.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-d" mid="93" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#662500>(Just as Vernicka thought.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>In return for letting him escape, she would have taken something that worked as a token of his death.<BR>That's how Lapis ended up surviving.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-e" mid="94" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#662500>A deal?</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>And the reason I discovered Lapis was still alive…<BR>Is that I made a deal with him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-f" mid="95" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>There was something I needed in the Red Waste, and I happened upon Lapis there.<BR>Because he is of royal blood, we at MHN were aware of what he looked like.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-g" mid="96" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>It turned out Lapis was hiding among the bandits in the citadel,<BR>and I figured it would be a help to Rhadames to be able to have a direct influence on their movements.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-h" mid="97" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#662500>Then that marked rock...</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>So we made a deal. I would keep Lapis' existence secret and<BR>he would watch the citadel bandits and make sure they never found Rhadames. We also agreed to meet at certain intervals.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-i" mid="98" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>That's the place we always meet.<BR>
That's how I have been protecting Rhadames from the citadel bandits.<BR>Now I have a favor to ask of you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-j" mid="99" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#662500>If the fact Lapis is still alive comes to light…</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>That Lapis still lives is a secret even to the rest of MHN. This becoming known would have serious consequences.<BR>I want you to keep quiet about everything you've learned about Lapis.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-k" mid="100" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT size=2 face=Arial>(Continue)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>Once a hidden card gets revealed, it makes sense to remove it from your hand as soon as possible.<BR>I'm sure they'll send someone to eliminate him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-l" mid="101" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rhadames is already in a tough spot with all these refugees.<BR>An attack by the citadel bandits would be most unwelcome at the moment.<BR>But… Vernicka already suspects that Lapis is still alive.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-l" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-m" mid="102" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>The problem is, President Vernicka already seems to have his doubts that Lapis is actually dead.<BR>If someone as powerful as the president asks me about Lapis, it will be hard not to tell the truth.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-n" mid="103" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>If that snake already suspects the truth, it will only be a matter of time before he finds out one way or another,<BR>even if you don't tell him outright.<BR>Still, just keeping quiet about the matter until then will give us the chance to come up with another plan.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-o" mid="104" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>In that case… All right.<BR>Rhadames has put in so much effort to avoid the clutches of the Childs and Goddess, so it would be a shame to have it attacked by those bandits...<BR>I won't tell anyone until the time comes.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-p" mid="105" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Manager Maisa$<BR>Thanks! And you did everything I asked, right? Guess it's time for a reward...<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rummages through pouch.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2964_meissa-5-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2964_meissa-5-q" mid="106" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Complete$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
