         <title mid="65"><![CDATA[Person Living in Silence]]></title>
         <contents mid="66"><![CDATA[<html>You did everything Lapis requested. It's time to return to Rhadames. Find Maisa and ask how it is that Lapis still lives, and also about their relationship.<BR><BR><FONT color=#086171>Rhadames</FONT> - <FONT color=#a82424>Manager Maisa</FONT></html>]]></contents>
         <destination mid="67"><![CDATA[Return to Manager Maisa]]></destination>
